---
description: Ensure the correct Node version is active before running any pnpm command.
alwaysApply: true
---

- If you run a pnpm command and see that you got an error about node, run nvm use then rerun the command.

<example>
pnpm test
error about node
nvm use && pnpm test
</example>
<example type="invalid">
Agent runs pnpm test without setting the Node version if the first run shows an error related to node version.
</example>
